Normal Distribution PDF

\[P(X) = \frac{1}{\sigma \sqrt {2\pi}}e^{-({x - \mu})^2 / {2\sigma ^2 }}\]

\[pdf(x,\mu,\sigma) = \frac{1}{ \sigma \sqrt{2 \pi}} e^{\left(-\frac{{\left(\mu - x\right)}^{2}}{2 \, \sigma^{2}}\right)}\]
